          | and improved efficiencies over centralized company systems. The main
          | hurdle of a decentralized system is for the system to gain enough users
          | to experience the benefits of decentralization. Drawing from our
          | experience in the advertising and promotion business we developed a
          | plan to bootstrap the system with tens/hundreds of thousands of active
          | users. See our User Acquisition section for detail.
